at”的VTuber。各种项目正在进行中，例如在 VRChat 游戏世界中玩耍、与其他玩家互动、制作一次性视频给粉丝带来惊喜。其特点是飞行、跳跃等，用全身积极活动，外形可爱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="专业人士讲解 VRC 物理" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SEVJCulO0nw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="如果我大便，视频就会结束" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kxgbtpUjPXA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-300x159.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-768x407.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1536x813.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="542" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-249661" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425